WEBVTT

00:01:53.777 --> 00:02:00.504
"Qish" konsertining kirish qismida
kimningdir tishlari sovuqdan chayqalmoqda

00:02:00.504 --> 00:02:07.283
keyin u otashin olov oldida
qo'nim topadi.

00:02:07.283 --> 00:02:09.264
Keyin yana bo'ron boshlanadi.

00:02:09.264 --> 00:02:15.165
Kimdir muz ustida sirpanadi va yiqiladi.

00:02:15.165 --> 00:02:18.315
Qishning dastlabki haftalarida
eski yil o'z nihoyasiga yetmoqda,

00:02:18.315 --> 00:02:23.175
Vivaldi ham shu nuqtada o'zining mavsumlar
bo'ylab sayohatiga yakun yasaydi.

00:02:23.175 --> 00:02:24.905
Qariyb XIX asrning boshlariga qadar

00:02:24.905 --> 00:02:28.305
bunday dasturga ega
ifodali cholg'u musiqasi

00:02:28.305 --> 00:02:30.386
ommabop emas edi.